st-language:EN-GB;\" lang=\"EN-US\" dir=\"ltr\">Failure to comply with the standard KEBS required weight may result in penalties leading to financial loss.</span></span></p>"], "required": false, "default_values": []}, {"id": "20511", "term": "Department", "value": null, "required": false, "default_values": []}, {"id": "20555", "term": "Objectives", "value": null, "required": false, "default_values": []}]}, "relationships": {"project": {"data": {"id": "125261", "type": "projects"}}, "owner_user": {"data": null}, "executive_owner_user": {"data": null}, "project_owner_user": {"data": null}, "creator_user": {"data": {"id": "V9z9xVxyss5vSmxPfyWs", "type": "users"}}}}, {"id": "575889", "type": "issues", "attributes": {"title": "Bread damages analysis", "description": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color:black;font-size:11.0pt;\"><span style=\"\">The review focused on ensuring compliance with the established damage thresholds, which are set at <strong>0.2%</strong> of total production for production-related damages and <strong>0.5%</strong> of total sales for market-related damages.</span><span style=\"\"></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\"><span>We noted the following:</span><b style=\"\"><strong></strong></b></span></p><ul>\n<li><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:57.0pt;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\"><span>Production damages stood at </span><b style=\"\"><span><strong>0.19%</strong></span></b><span> of total production which was within the set limit of 0.2%</span><b style=\"\"><strong></strong></b></span></p></li>\n<li><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:57.0pt;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\"><span>Market damages stood at </span><b style=\"\"><span><strong>0.44%</strong></span></b><span> of total sales, which was within the set limit of <strong>0.5%</strong></span></span></p></li>\n</ul><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:57.0pt;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\"><b style=\"\"><strong></strong></b></span></p>", "creator_name": "Nelly Chepkorir", "created_at": "2025-02-04T10:31:59Z", "updated_at": "2025-02-04T10:31:59Z", "position": 4, "owner": "Branch manager", "recommendation": "<div style=\"\">\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\"><span>Maintain the controls in place and improve further.</span></span></p>\n<p><span style='font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;font-size:11.0pt;'><span style=\"\">Branch management should ensure proper recording of damages to eliminate variances between expected damages and those sent to the ingredient department</span></span></p>\n</div>", "deficiency_type": "Management Recommendation", "severity": "Medium", "published": true, "identified_at": "2025-02-04T00:00:00Z", "reference": null, "reference_prefix": "03", "risk": null, "scope": null, "escalation": null, "cause": "", "effect": "", "cost_impact": null, "executive_summary": null, "executive_owner": null, "project_owner": null, "closed": false, "remediation_status": null, "remediation_plan": null, "remediation_date": null, "actual_remediation_date": null, "retest_deadline_date": null, "actual_retest_date": null, "retesting_results_overview": null, "custom_attributes": [{"id": "20317", "term": "Management  Comments 1", "value": ["<div style=\"mso-element-anchor-horizontal:column;mso-element-anchor-vertical:paragraph;mso-element-frame-hspace:9.0pt;mso-element-left:right;mso-element-top:.05pt;mso-element-wrap:around;mso-element:frame;mso-height-rule:exactly;\"><p><span style=\"font-family:Symbol;font-size:11.0pt;\"><span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-list:Ignore;\" lang=\"EN-US\" dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" dir=\"ltr\">Production and market damages are within the set limit.</span></span></p></div>"], "required": false, "default_values": []}, {"id": "20318", "term": "Management Comments 2", "value": ["<p><span style=\"color:black;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;font-size:11.0pt;\"><span style=\"layout-grid-mode:line;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB;\" lang=\"EN-US\" dir=\"ltr\">We will strengthen the controls to ensure proper recording of damages to ensure no variances are noted.</span></span></p>"], "required": false, "default_values": []}, {"id": "20319", "term": "Follow-up Findings", "value": ["<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"tab-stops:117.0pt 200.95pt;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" dir=\"ltr\">In prior audit dated 09/12/2024, It was found that production bread damages were averaging at </span><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" dir=\"ltr\"><strong>0.19% </strong></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" dir=\"ltr\">of the production and market damages stood at </span><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" dir=\"ltr\"><strong>0.58%</strong></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" dir=\"ltr\"> of the sales.</span><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;\"><strong><o:p></o:p></strong></b></span></p>"], "required": false, "default_values": []}, {"id": "20488", "term": "Current / Previous finding", "value": null, "required": false, "default_values": []}, {"id": "20507", "term": "Introduction ", "value": null, "required": false, "default_values": []}, {"id": "20508", "term": "Conclusion", "value": null, "required": false, "default_values": []}, {"id": "20511", "term": "Department", "value": ["Operations/Production Department"], "required": false, "default_values": []}, {"id": "20555", "term": "Objectives", "value": null, "required": false, "default_values": []}]}, "relationships": {"project": {"data